- `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-142750/light-embed/.claude/CLAUDE.md` — Project overview
- `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-142750/light-embed/.claude/skills/entity-skill/SKILL.md` — Entity/Repository patterns
- `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-142750/light-embed/.claude/skills/develop/SKILL.md` — Development workflow
- `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-142750/light-embed/.claude/skills/grpc-skill/SKILL.md` — gRPC implementation guide
- `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-142750/light-embed/.claude/skills/graphql-skill/SKILL.md` — GraphQL implementation guide
- `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-142750/light-embed/.claude/skills/test-skill/SKILL.md` — Testing patterns

